title: The Shrine x Barrett Avner - "Rare Breed" - In The Studio
description:
"Rare Breed" was produced by Eliminator with music by The Shrine and Barrett Avner, lyrics by Josh Landau and vocals by The Shrine. The track was recorded at Eliminator Studios in Los Angeles, California and is the fourth track on the Converse compilation CONS EP VOL. 1.

Produced by: Eliminator
Music by: The Shrine and Barrett Avner
Lyrics by: Josh Landau
Vocals by: The Shrine
